<SYNC Start=408196><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=409598><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
♫너만 보면 그래
<SYNC Start=414550><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=416098><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
