<SYNC Start=477190><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=478610><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
없잖아요, 방법이.
<SYNC Start=481180><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=482560><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
지금으로서는요.
<SYNC Start=484110><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=484110><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
어쨌든 직접 죽인 건 아니니까요.
<SYNC Start=487510><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=488570><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
버렸을지 몰라도.
<SYNC Start=491260><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=492190><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그렇죠?
<SYNC Start=494020><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=514210><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
