<SYNC Start=827690><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=828990><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
아니.
<SYNC Start=830650><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=832530><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
