<SYNC Start=847630><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=847650><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그건
<SYNC Start=848950><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=850710><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
