<SYNC Start=860890><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=860900><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
죽었기를 바랐구나.
<SYNC Start=862530><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=862540><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
아니야.
<SYNC Start=864130><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=865630><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
아니야, 민아.
<SYNC Start=867480><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=868080><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
날 알아보지도 못했어.
<SYNC Start=870490><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=874830><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그래.
<SYNC Start=876290><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=880630><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
