<SYNC Start=897800><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=899230><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
이준영한테
<SYNC Start=901360><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=901800><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
