<SYNC Start=947560><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=947760><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
근데
<SYNC Start=949410><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=950560><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
근데
<SYNC Start=951900><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=952030><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
진짜 괴물은 내 동생 민이에요.
<SYNC Start=958000><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=963460><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
