<SYNC Start=3229890><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3229890><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
이준호 쌤 차 타고. 우연히 만났거든.
<SYNC Start=3233560><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3235030><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
이준호?
<SYNC Start=3236130><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3236860><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
있지, 이준호 선생님이.
<SYNC Start=3240530><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3243840><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
