<SYNC Start=3253770><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3254740><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
문단속 잘해.
<SYNC Start=3256520><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3257240><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
걱정 마. 당신이나 조심하고.
<SYNC Start=3260900><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3262710><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
