<SYNC Start=3338040><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3338530><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
뭐가요?
<SYNC Start=3339850><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3340400><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
특정 사람한테 특별한 관심 갖는 거.
<SYNC Start=3345140><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3346270><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
