<SYNC Start=3410840><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3412150><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
아.
<SYNC Start=3413340><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3414140><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
