<SYNC Start=3425140><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3428600><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그래서 그랬구나.
<SYNC Start=3430390><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3432120><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
