<SYNC Start=3452050><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3452160><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
근데 좀 이상하지.
<SYNC Start=3453970><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3454150><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
