<SYNC Start=3502590><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3502590><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그렇지.
<SYNC Start=3503700><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3506180><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
