<SYNC Start=3578470><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3578570><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
살아서 소중한 상대가<br>
잔혹하게 죽는 걸 봐야
<SYNC Start=3584810><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3586120><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
